---
import Base from "../layouts/base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="What You'll Get (and When)"
  description="What do you get with our support plans and when do you get it"
  type="WebPage"
  canonicalURL="https://getclarity.win/what-you-get"
>
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold mb-4">What You'll Get (and When)</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
      Clarity. isn't a deliverable. It's a continuous support that compounds.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section
    class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-24 text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 space-y-10"
  >
    <p class="text-center">
      Clarity. isn't a workshop, a report, or a one-off engagement. <br />
      It's a cadence — one that helps you make better decisions, faster, and with
      more confidence.
    </p>

    <p class="text-center">
      Our Support Plans aren't based on time or deliverables. <br />
      They're built around how embedded we are in your world — and how much strategic
      momentum you want.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section
    class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-gray-900 text-white dark:bg-black/50 rounded-lg px-8 py-12 mb-24 text-center"
  >
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Your First 90 Days</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-left text-sm md:text-base">
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">
          Days 1-30 → Immediate Traction
        </h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
          <li>Fast onboarding</li>
          <li>Clear, structured starting point</li>
          <li>Tangible outputs from day one</li>
        </ul>
        <blockquote class="italic text-blue-200 mt-2">
          “You leave the first cycle with momentum, not more questions.”
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">
          Days 31-60 → Strategic Rhythm
        </h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
          <li>Cadence is set and starts compounding</li>
          <li>
            Consistency with prioritisation, blockers, and surfacing opportunity
          </li>
          <li>We work around your real-world pace</li>
        </ul>
        <blockquote class="italic text-blue-200 mt-2">
          “Your decisions start aligning. Your team starts accelerating.”
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">
          Days 61-90 → Compounding Value
        </h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
          <li>We're embedded in your world</li>
          <li>Faster recommendations, sharper context</li>
          <li>Radar picks up issues early</li>
        </ul>
        <blockquote class="italic text-blue-200 mt-2">
          “You spend less time explaining everything again and more time moving
          forward.”
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-24 text-left">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">Included in Every Plan</h2>
    <div
      class="flex flex-col h-full p-6 rounded-lg text-left"
    >
      <ul
        class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 text-sm md:text-base list-disc list-outside"
      >
        <li>
          <strong>Expert Insight, Applied Experience</strong> - Clear, confident
          direction from people who've done this before, and know what works.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Aligned Priorities, Fewer Delays</strong> - We help you focus fast,
          unblock momentum, and move with intent.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong> Decision-Making Support</strong> - No more circling. We frame
          the choices, flag the risks, and guide you forward.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Proactive Partnership</strong> - You don't need to chase us. We
          lead the cadence and show up ready.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Forward Visibility</strong> - You'll know what's coming, what to
          watch for, and how to stay ahead.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-24 px-4">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">
      Choosing the Right Support Plan
    </h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 items-stretch text-sm md:text-base">
      <!-- Base -->
      <div
        class="flex flex-col h-full p-6 border rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-black/20 text-left"
      >
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-3 text-center">Clarity. Base</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-outside pl-5 space-y-2">
          <li>For teams starting small or validating one area.</li>
          <li>Quick traction, clear priorities, light support.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Plus -->
      <div
        class="flex flex-col h-full p-6 border rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-black/20 text-left"
      >
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-3 text-center">Clarity. Plus</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-outside pl-5 space-y-2">
          <li>
            For product and platform leaders juggling multiple moving parts.
          </li>
          <li>Ongoing prioritisation, insight, and sharper decisions.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Partner -->
      <div
        class="flex flex-col h-full p-6 border rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-black/20 text-left"
      >
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-3 text-center">Clarity. Partner</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-outside pl-5 space-y-2">
          <li>For high-velocity orgs or complex portfolios.</li>
          <li>
            Proactive support, deeper embeddedness, and foresight you can act
            on.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <blockquote
      class="italic text-center mt-6 text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-300"
    >
      “Not sure? Start small. Most clients scale up once they feel the support.”
    </blockquote>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-24 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Why Support Plans Work</h2>
    <div class="overflow-x-auto">
      <table
        class="table-auto w-full text-left border-collapse text-sm md:text-base"
      >
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th class="px-4 py-2 font-semibold">Traditional Models</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-2 font-semibold">Clarity. Support Plans</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td class="px-4 py-2 border-t">Scope-driven</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-2 border-t">Cadence-driven</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="px-4 py-2 border-t">Time-based billing</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-2 border-t">Value-based continuous support</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="px-4 py-2 border-t">Outputs you need to re-explain</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-2 border-t">Momentum that builds</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="px-4 py-2 border-t">Individuals-based</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-2 border-t">Continuity built-in</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Navigation Arrows -->
  <section class="my-16 flex flex-col items-center gap-4 text-center">
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
      Got some unanswered questions? Check out the FAQ.
    </p>
    <div class="flex gap-12 justify-center items-center">
      <!-- Left Arrow Link -->
      <a
        href="/why-clarity-works"
        aria-label="Previous page"
        class="hover:text-blue-600 transition"
      >
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          width="64"
          height="64"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path>
        </svg>
      </a>

      <!-- Right Arrow Link -->
      <a
        href="/faq"
        aria-label="Next page"
        class="hover:text-blue-600 transition"
      >
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          width="64"
          height="64"
        >
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"
          ></path>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="text-center mb-24">
    <h2 class="text-xl mb-4 font-semibold">Still unsure?</h2>
    <p class="mb-4 text-lg">You don't have to guess.</p>
    <a
      href="/"
      class="inline-block bg-black text-white dark:bg-white dark:text-black font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded hover:opacity-90 transition"
    >
      Join the Waitlist
    </a>
  </div>
</Base>
